name: Cheese Quest (Vinny Does Gamez)
description:
You play as Terry and you are on a mission take take the cheese back from the aliens who stole it! You also team up with your friend, Chad. He runs a YouTube prank channel that is just completely awful. You also team up with Steven, the guardian of the forest. He is a very mysterious bird man. You also team up with Kid. He is a Kid. There are even more wacky characters to meet that you don't team up with! There are also some great songs on the soundtrack, such as Chad Battle, AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA, All Star, and so much more! I had a ton of fun making this and I hope you have fun playing this. 

Average playthrough 2 - 4 hours
